{"type": "article", "id": 3555, "title": "三星发了说唱版报告，槽点多到不能直视", "description": "每次三星都能突破你的底线，如此轻而易举。", "date": "2014-11-14T10:22:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 536, "name": "三星"}, {"id": 4265, "name": "可持续报告"}, {"id": 536, "name": "三星"}, {"id": 4265, "name": "可持续报告"}], "category": 4, "author": 1741, "comment_count": 20, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604215521nCdbgZrwcB1tmWAI.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">把枯燥的报告写成说唱歌曲，再配上时兴的定格动画，是希望借流行文化营销自己</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">。不过三星这么做，就<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">让事情从有趣上升到不忍直视。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t事情开始于三星年初发布的一份《可持续发展报告》，这份报告中漂亮的多样性数据和糟糕的管理数据被摆在了一起。在强调三星男女员工比例是 6：4 的同时，也坦白它就是没有管好生产设备，违规使用在多数情况下都不能被及时纠正。看了这样的数据，投资者和消费者还能为前者感到欢欣鼓舞吗？\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t仿佛觉得这样还不够令人忧心，三星本周又<a href=\"http://9to5google.com/2014/11/12/samsung-made-a-rap-video-about-its-sustainability-report-and-its-awful/\" target=\"_blank\">把报告中好看的数字挑了挑，写了一首糟糕的说唱歌曲放进去</a>。这回大家都傻眼了：这首《可持续报告之管理才能》把“管理才能”<span>简化成了企业女员工比例高，对孕妇照顾得好，还雇佣残疾人员工。而且歌词里这些句子常常压不住韵脚，让你在听三星避重就轻营销自己的同时，对它的品味产生担忧。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135334gqyB15VU6Gn9frRJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.33425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">三星实际上把《可持续报告》之歌做成了一个系列，不过发布不久之后，众人吐槽的口水眼看就要漫过堤坝，三星慌忙撤了 Youtube 上的视频</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">，对后续也低调处理了</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t现在来一起欣赏一下这只<a href=\"http://time.com/3581660/weird-samsung-rap-video/\" target=\"_blank\">三星说唱出的《可持续报告》</a>（请在 TIME 官网观看）。不是投资人我们可以一起开心一下，投资人请自行角落里哭泣。以下是歌词及翻译。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Here we go once\r\nagain </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">YOYOYO\r\n走起来</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Samsung to the\r\nrescue </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">三星又来救火了</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Put wings to your\r\ndreams </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">在这里梦能圆</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Everyone just listen </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">你们听我说</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Samsung we two\r\nhundred </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">我们有二十八</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Eighty thousand\r\nhumans </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">万人</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Forty percent of 100 </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">十个之中有四个</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Twelve thousand\r\nwomen </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">女性</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">That don’t have to\r\nworry </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">她们想生孩子就能生</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">After giving birth </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">甩手就能不干活</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Sit back, relax, no\r\nneed to work </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">做这个不亏（担）心</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">It’s all taken care of </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">剩下的交给男人</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Live it up through us </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">和不想这么干的女人</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Family friendly company </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">多么温馨的公司</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">With kindergarten approval </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">提前下班接孩子</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">So many good employments </span><span></span>还招人</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Waiting for you </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">招好多</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Finding people with\r\ngreat skills </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">技术好又有才？</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">And talents too </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">快来</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Sign up for Samsung\r\nSoftware Membership </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">软件组等你</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Have talent for\r\ndesign </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">会设计不一般？</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Go to Samsung Design\r\nMembership </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">设计组注册</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Samsung’s all for\r\ndiversity </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">三星看重多样性</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">We having that\r\nfoothold internship </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">折翼的天使</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">For the student of\r\nhandicap </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">也欢迎（实习）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Making dreams come\r\ntrue </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">在这里梦能圆</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">All the\r\npossibilities of what you want </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">全是可能性</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">We can do it all for\r\nyou </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">我们耕种</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">We just letting our\r\ndreams come true </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">你收获</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Make it shine </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">三星好了</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Let us smile </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">一起笑</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Samsung will be\r\nthere </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">三星要</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Global harmony with\r\npeople </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">和谐人类</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Society and\r\nenvironment </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">社会、环境</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Samsung. </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">和自己</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t（Drops mic 放话筒）\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215520Is2Z1aRgLtlJMrVG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t题图来自：<a href=\"http://www.qigaipo.com/vso-%E6%9A%B4%E8%B5%B0%E6%BC%AB%E7%94%BB%E5%A3%81%E7%BA%B8.html\" target=\"_blank\">Baozou Comics</a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}